Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:45.46,Captions,,0,0,300,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Ten years after their departure from Twin Capes\N-The Florian Triangle-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw you taking off your pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Kidding! How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Having so much fun~! I'm alone, but I'm having so much fun~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,45 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:07.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Aha, look at this, someone! Ah, I am all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook! How long are you gonna sleep, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wake up, we've spotted an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.30,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a summer island! A beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... Huh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh? No, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.53,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're not here, we can't start, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... You are all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? I am so glad... Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:49.85,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you be alive? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying? How long are you gonna keep dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,If it hurts, that must mean this isn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,This is real! That other part must have been the dream! Thank G-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:28.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Captain Yorki managed to get through the Calm Belt safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess only the ocean knows that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:35.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to carry on, for his sake!\NTake this new ship onward, to where Laboon's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,It is morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,We're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a huge storm! The sail's gonna be torn to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hah! We just have to sing and ride it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, Brook! Look at this!\NYou've got yourself a bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What's this?! Keep playing, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!! I was dancing with chopsticks in my nose!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Please wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Awesome~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN DO THAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,This is called a Tone Dial... I bought it from a merchant ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:31.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a very rare kind of shell that can record sound and play it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, those things from Sky Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.68,Main,,0,0,0,,You are familiar with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:42.05,Main,,0,0,0,,When I meet Laboon again, I plan on letting him hear this. I always keep it on my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got something recorded on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It is a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the voice of my crewmates singing, back when they were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:55.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Something to let him know that we were all happy right to the end of our journey. A message to Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.91,Main,,0,0,0,,May I play it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:01.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanna hear it! I'm sure Laboon would love to hear it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,How... many of us... are still breathing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We're breathing... but it doesn't seem like there's any hope for any of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've got ourselves wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Their weapons were... poisoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Seems like we're all gonna die, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,We're pirates, so we were prepared to die at any time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.98,Main,,0,0,0,,we didn't think we'd all die at once...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Brook... About that Revive Fruit of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:53.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knows... I have never died before, but... I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:56.53,Main,,0,0,0,,We will die anyway, so let us die while having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we sing a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:07.14,Main,,0,0,0,,If the power of the Revive Fruit really will bring me back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,then I will deliver it to him without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,The Tone Dial...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,This song that Laboon, the captain, and all of us loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:22.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Waiting for us at that cape, not knowing whether we will come today or tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Our comrade.... I will deliver it to Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... You guys... Let's not fall until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Let him hear it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's give Laboon the Rumbar Pirates' once-in-a-lifetime performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? If it's this song, then we'll all join in, too!
