Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What is wrong? Now, this is just a quartet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Trio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:18.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Duet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Solo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:32.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? Leaving just the accompaniment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:37.48,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,If you wanna join my crew, all I ask is that you love music!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:41.64,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,This is the ship of the Rumbar Pirates, who can even make a crying child laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:48.17,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Laboon! We will definitely return here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.03,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:25.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Laboon... You have waited there for fifty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:30.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,But can you wait for just another year or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:38.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,For I, too, have the true spirit of a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:42.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,You are facing that wall and waiting for me... And just as we promised, when I meet you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:45.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'll be coming over that wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Is the song over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Give us another one! Just one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:05.19,Main,,0,0,0,,The song I once sung with my comrades, who were so full of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Was the final performance of the Rumbar Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,During the fifty years when I was drifting alone in that dark, dark, sea of mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,How many times did I listen to this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,On that vast ship, all on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,this song was the only thing that made me feel that there was life besides my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,However, today, I have finally found new conviction in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,So I shall seal away this Tone Dial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.32,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAAAAT?! SO YOU REALLY CAN DO THAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:58.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I now know that Laboon is still safe, and waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,And I have gotten my shadow back, and can escape from these cursed waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,This Dial, with everyone's voices recorded upon it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:11.70,Main,,0,0,0,,is no longer going to be used so I can think back on the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It is a song for Laboon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Every day was painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I was truly unable to see any hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,But, now, Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I am so glad to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:38.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I truly am glad to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Finally, this day has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,May I join your crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT?! JUST LIKE THAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,HE JOINED?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,But, whatever! We've got our musician! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,A musician! He's just bones, but he's our musician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The musician we've always wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:17.19,Main,,0,0,0,,He's so light, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,That lightness is another thing that's great about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! Because I am just bones~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,He's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:28.64,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Just bones! Just bones! Just bones! Just bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,They certainly are very lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do we keep gathering up people like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand, but they seem happy, don't they, Namizou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't get it at all, but cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:47.16,Main,,0,0,0,,We have no idea, but cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,45 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:58.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:08.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,I will not turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:12.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,We always pushed on, straight forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:17.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,That path was the only one we could take in order to come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:21.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,To travel around the world was our goal, and you were waiting at the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:27.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Right? So I will not turn back.\NI will carry on, and see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Please wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:35.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,It will just be a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:17:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You're in a really good mood today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,A wanted-poster? You had a bounty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I have still not introduced myself properly... I am "Dead Bones", and my name is Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I am a wanted man... My title is "Humming Brook"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,My current bounty is 33 million bellies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Once the leader of an escort convoy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,and afterwards, musician and swordsman, and eventually acting Captain, of the Rumbar Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:45.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I offer my services and my life to captain Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope not to be a burden to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I shall work myself to the bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:18:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's have one more toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.23,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(500,0)}Two days later
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Magnificent! Thank you so much, Franky-san, Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,No problem at all! This was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,My design was a great success!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I picked the flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What a magnificent grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, I couldn't possibly expect you to bring all those bones with you on Lion-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Call it the Thousand Sunny next time, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,So strange that this Thriller Bark should have come from our own homeland, West Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But here, in the earth of our homeland, they might at last be able to rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, Brook, we'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:54.58,Secondary,,0,0,0,,We'll be going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.66,Secondary,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, that surprised me. So, you have finally recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I just overslept a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:32.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a dead sword... Yubashiri.\NI was gonna give it a proper burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:39.77,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Luffy is the man who is gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, that is right, I became a part of your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh, is that so? Well, you've got bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a pretty crazy crew, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems that way. I will do my best until I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, but I am already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,OK! Now that Zoro's awake, let's head out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's head off to our next adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:19.01,Main,,0,0,0,,YEAH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Zoro, you took off your bandages again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, 'cause they're hard to move around in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I put them there so you wouldn't move around so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:29.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:32.44,Main,,0,0,0,,He sure recovered quickly. Are you already setting sail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You can take Brook's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I fixed the helm and the sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:40.88,Main,,0,0,0,,After all you've done, we're really indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,We couldn't thank you enough no matter how hard we tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You seem like a nice lady, but I'm afraid I'm far too super for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a real shame to see you guys go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you stay and party for just a few more days?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! We're going to Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet we'll meet some funny guys there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:08.74,Main,,0,0,0,,And some beautiful mermaids! Ah, what I wouldn't love to do with one of them~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:13.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the mermaids will let me see their panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:20.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Mermaids don't wear panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,While we're talking about how beautiful mermaids are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:28.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I hear even the Pirate Empress Hancock was totally overwhelmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Mermaids~! Mermaids~!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:34.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Surely they have tails instead of legs anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you guys know that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, about three years ago, before we came here, we went to Fishman Island! That place is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:46.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Lola, you guys went to the New World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't go there! We were born in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,My mama was a pirate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:58.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my mama's Vivrecard. I'll let you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain Lola's mama is a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:10.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Take good care of it! It'll definitely be useful later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:13.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What's a Vivrecard?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:18.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain Lola, they only make Vivrecards in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:22.62,Main,,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:25.34,Main,,0,0,0,,It's resistant to both fire and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What you do is you take a few of your own fingernails to a shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,and they use them to make you a special sheet of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:35.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That is the "Card of Life", the Vivrecard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What you do, is you tear off pieces and give them to friends or family if they're going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the Vivrecard my mama gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:48.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:51.66,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter where in the world the Card pieces are, they share a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:55.45,Main,,0,0,0,,So I can always tell in what direction my mama is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Although you can't tell how far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:22:59.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, so mysterious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:02.69,Main,,0,0,0,,And they have lots of them in the New World, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,It's quite convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll just sign this piece of my Mama's Vivrecard for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:11.57,Main,,0,0,0,,If you ever run into trouble, just follow this and go see Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,And be sure to tell her that I'm doing fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I've got one of those, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.98,0:23:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I just thought of that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't this just like that white piece of paper Ace gave you back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:28.24,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,This piece of paper will allow us to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,So, that's what he meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's burning, and seems like it's gotten smaller...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, you! Let me see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:47.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is certainly a Vivrecard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:53.72,Main,,0,0,0,,But I didn't tell you this yet... This paper also reflects the owner's vitality and life force!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,This belonged to someone important to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:59.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's my brother's!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Lola?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:12.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell you, but this person's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.06,0:24:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,is fading!
